OL,3,CShields Ferry services to return after
OL,4,Clanding was damaged by storm
OL,6,FThe Shields Ferry will return to
OL,7,Fservice from Monday 27 April,
OL,8,Ffollowing repair work on the north
OL,9,Flanding.
OL,11,FThe North Shields landing was damaged
OL,12,Fduring Storm Chandra back on 29
OL,13,FJanuary and had been closed as a
OL,14,Fsafety precaution, while essential
OL,15,Frepairs were carried out.
OL,17,FOperator Nexus said it was pleased to
OL,18,Fbe getting crossings back up and
OL,19,Frunning and thanked customers for
OL,20,Ftheir patience during the temporary
OL,21,Fclosure.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
