PN,42302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1777050358
OL,3,CShields Ferry services to return after
OL,4,Clanding was damaged by storm
OL,6,FThe monitoring equipment added to the
OL,7,Flanding will observe any noticeable
OL,8,Fmovement and will identify if any
OL,9,Ffuture temporary suspensions of the
OL,10,Fservice need to happen.
OL,12,FCathy Massarella, Managing Director of
OL,13,FNexus, said: "I'm very pleased to
OL,14,Fconfirm that the Shields Ferry will be
OL,15,Freturning to service next week.
OL,17,F"This will come into effect from
OL,18,FMonday (27 April) at 6.45am at our
OL,19,FSouth Shields landing. A normal
OL,20,Ftimetable will be in place.
OL,26,@uD@NOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
