OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1777050358
OL,3,CShields Ferry services to return after
OL,4,Clanding was damaged by storm
OL,6,F"As always, safety is our top priority
OL,7,Fand we're confident we're in a place
OL,8,Fto welcome back the public. However,
OL,9,Fthe landing remains an aged asset. The
OL,10,Fwork we've carried out prolongs its
OL,11,Fuse, but people can be reassured we
OL,12,Fare keeping a very close eye on the
OL,13,Fstructure using this monitoring
OL,14,Fequipment.
OL,16,F"My thanks go to our customers and the
OL,17,Fwider community that the Ferry serves
OL,18,Ffor their patience during the service
OL,19,Fsuspension. "
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
